        "col3_Name of plan and URL link, if applicable^": "「ゼロエミッション東京戦略」 https://www.kankyo.metro.tokyo.lg.jp/documents/d/kankyo/zeroemission_tokyo-strategy-files-zero_emission_tokyo_strategy \\n「ゼロエミッション東京戦略2020 Update & Report」 https://www.kankyo.metro.tokyo.lg.jp/documents/d/kankyo/zeroemission_tokyo-strategy_2020update-files-zero_emission_tokyo_2020update_report \\n「2030年カーボンハーフに向けた取組の加速 -Fast forward to “Carbon Half”-」https://www.kankyo1.metro.tokyo.lg.jp/dbook/202202/carbonhalf/2022-02_tokyo_carbonhalf/#page1\\n ゼロエミッション東京戦略 beyond カーボンハーフ\\nhttps://www.kankyo1.metro.tokyo.lg.jp/dbook/202504/zeroemission-tokyo-beyond-carbon-half/#page=1\\nhttps://www.kankyo.metro.tokyo.lg.jp/documents/d/kankyo/full-ver-ze-strategy0311 https://www.kankyo.metro.tokyo.lg.jp/documents/d/kankyo/zeroemissionstrategy_update202106 https://www.kankyo1.metro.tokyo.lg.jp/dbook/202202/carbonhalf/2022-02_tokyo_carbonhalf/book.pdf\\nhttps://www.kankyo.metro.tokyo.lg.jp/documents/d/kankyo/zeroemission-tokyo-beyond-carbon-half-e-summary-hp-pdf-1\\n",
        "col4_Confirm attachment/link provided to plan": "The plan can be accessed (unrestricted) on the link provided",
        "col5_Boundary of plan relative to jurisdiction boundary": "Same (jurisdiction-wide) - covers entire jurisdiction and nothing else",
